item.title: My moparscape cilent wont load servers?
item.dc:creator: @crakaman crakaman
item.description:
@crakaman wrote:

Well one the server might have a different port so you can switch that by clicking file>new port put in the port there most have default one that mopar starts with which is 43594, than second the server could be down many servers are usually down not all are up most of the time. and third some are hamachi servers hope that helped
